text.en: You can target 1 monster on the field; banish it, then return it to the field. If your opponent activates a card or effect: You can target 1 face-up monster whose effects are negated; banish it, then return it to the field. Before resolving an opponent's card effect that targets this face-up card, banish this card until the End Phase of the next turn. You can only use each effect of "Interdimensional Matter Translocator" once per turn.
